window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It’s the holidays at Roman’s ranch, but behind the idyllic set-up,</b><br> <b>a storm is brewing all around Eve…</b><br> <br> After two hikers go missing in a snowstorm,<br> Sheriff Eve Wicker is fighting against all odds to bring them to safety.<br> When she gets a phone call from her boss that leaves her rattled.<br> She heads to the office to discuss a past case with Jamison.<br> <br> While the storm brews both outside and in her life, the rescue party amidst the dangerous blizzard leads Eve to a cabin.<br> The hidden cabin is a blood-soaked crime scene, with the dead body of one of the hikers inside.<br> It seems a killer with an axe got to one of them first.<br> <br> <b><i>Each clue pulls on threads that leads her to the most shocking revelation.</i></b><br> <b><i>Deadly storms, dangerous terrain, and a murderer with an axe to grind.</i></b><br> <b><i>The hidden cabin is harboring many deadly secrets.</i></b></p>"; 
